ygData.messageBody:
I have the same question.

I am Trej.

You can find me on Saryrn and on Veeshan some nights after 8PM CDT.

/who all trej usually turns me up....heh heh or ask anyone in Ring of
Shadows guild.

Ring of Shadows on Saryrn likes to help new and upcoming players, so ask any
questions or find me online and I will help ya out as much as I can...

Trejulial Satisdee...37th lvl Dark Elf Enchanter (this is my main character,
but I have many alts...)
